          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Domestic Research Enhancement Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a research tax credit for 35% of in-house research expenses (contracted research expenses), including any research funded by any grant or contract or&nbsp;by another person or governmental entity.</p>]]></text>
